column4: A summer uniform reimagined in breathable Egyptian cotton poplin. This set includes a short-sleeved shirt and tailored shorts, both cut for a relaxed fit that moves easily with you. The shirt features a soft spread collar, button closure, and a single chest pocket for subtle utility. The shorts are designed with short legs, an elastic waistband with tonal drawstring, discreet side pockets, and a single back pocket. Lightweight, easy to wear, and endlessly versatile, made for warm days at home or in the city. Made in Egypt.
